---
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';

---
<html >
<body >
  <Navigation />
  <br>
  <script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/flowbite@2.5.1/dist/flowbite.min.js"></script>
  <div class="acctcontainer" ></div>
  <div class="text">
    <h1> Accounting Services</h1>
  </div>
<main>
<div class="acctcontainer">
  <div class="image">
    <img src="../images/Accounting.jpg" alt="SinghCPA" class="responsive-image">
  </div>
  <div class="text">
	<p> At Singh CPA Inc, We offer comprehensive accounting services designed to meet the distinct needs of individuals, small businesses, and corporations. From precise financial reporting to forward-thinking strategic guidance, our certified professionals 
		are committed to helping you maintain compliance, optimize performance, and achieve long-term financial health.
	</p>
         <br><br>
    <br>  
  </div>
</div>
<div class="acctcontainer">
	<div class="text">
	  <h4>We offer the following tax services:</h4>
	  <br>
	  <h4>1. Bookkeeping</h4>
	  <p>
		Accurate and timely bookkeeping is essential for sound business decisions. Our team handles all 
		aspects of daily financial recording so you can focus on growing your business.
	  </p>
	  <h4>Our services include:</h4>
	  <ul class="services-list">
		<li>Transaction recording</li>
		<li>Bank and credit card reconciliations</li>
		<li>General ledger maintenance</li>
		<li>Accounts receivable and payable tracking</li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
  </div>
</div>
</main>
  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 800px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	.astro-a {
		position: absolute;
		top: -32px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translatex(-50%);
		width: 220px;
		height: auto;
		z-index: -1;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		color: white;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: rem;
		font-weight: 100;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: left;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		color: white;
	}
	.text-gradient {
		background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(48ch, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 0;
	}
	.center {
  		display: block;
  		margin-left: auto;
  		margin-right: auto;
  		width: 50%;
	}
	html {
    background-color: rgb(28, 0, 128);
    font-family: sans-serif;
  }
  .acctcontainer {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start; /* Align items to the top */
  justify-content: flex-start; /* Align content to the left */
  gap: 20px; /* Adds space between the image and text */
  flex-wrap: wrap; /* Ensures responsiveness on smaller screens */
}

.image {
  flex: 1; /* Allows the image to take up available space */
  text-align: center; /* Centers the image */
}

.responsive-image {
  max-width: 100%; /* Ensures the image doesn't exceed its container */
  height: auto; /* Maintains the aspect ratio */
  border-radius: 10px; /* Optional: Adds rounded corners */
}

.text {
  flex: 2; /* Allows the text to take up more space than the image */
  font-size: 15px;
  color: white;
  text-align: left; /* Aligns the text to the left */
}
.services-list {
  list-style: disc; /* Adds bullet points */
  padding-left: 20px; /* Adds indentation for the bullets */
  margin-top: 10px; /* Adds spacing above the list */
  color: white; /* Ensures the text color is consistent */
  font-size: 15px; /* Adjusts the font size for readability */
}

.services-list li {
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem; /* Adds spacing between list items */
}

.text h4 {
  font-size: 18px; /* Adjusts the heading size */
  font-weight: bold; /* Makes the heading bold */
  margin-bottom: 10px; /* Adds spacing below the heading */
}

.text p {
  font-size: 15px; /* Adjusts the paragraph font size */
  line-height: 1.6; /* Improves readability */
  margin-bottom: 15px; /* Adds spacing below the paragraph */
}
</style>